#Artvatars Funeral Home
###Artvatars Interred Here: 284
Out of respect for the departed, please refrain from right-clicking.

NFTs are dead. Here lie the Artvatars. Gone but never forgotten.


###About

  - Created through a collaboration of over sixty of the world's top crypto artists, Artvatars are one-of-a-kind works of art created from infinite possibilities. Each Artvatar is uniquely composed from the artists' works, spliced into components and assembled by an AI algorithm. 

  - An Artvatar can have up to twelve unique features: Forehead, eyes, ears, mouth, shoulders, frame and background are standard components; hair, mustache, hat and glasses are optional and do not always appear.  

  Very rarely, an Artvatar will have a "special" attribute. See if you can spot any :)

###Score and Rarity

  - Each Artvatar has a Score determined by its components. The value of each component is hidden, but it's roughly based on the corresponding artist's NFT sales (as of early 2021). An Artvatar's Score is simply the sum of the values of its components. 

  - Rarity is derived from the Score: 0-588 is "Common" | 589-649 is "Uncommon"  
650-725 is "Rare" | 726-799 is "Legendary" | 800+ is "Mythic"

####Only 6,720 Artvatars exist. Some have been burned. No more will ever be created.

### www.artvatars.com | @artvatars | discord.gg/artvatars

###Gallery Randomizer

Hang out for a minute to load the images. 
If it doesn't work, leave the parcel and come back, or try refreshing.

Enjoy!
